\n###LINK###\n\nTo keep your site safe, this link will expire in ###EXPIRES###. Don't worry about that, though: a new link will be emailed to you if the error occurs again after it expires.\n\nWhen seeking help with this issue, you may be asked for some of the following information:\n###DEBUG###\n\n###DETAILS###":["Howdy!\n\nWordPress has a built-in feature that detects when a Plugin or \u00c0k\u00f2r\u00ed causes a fatal error on your \u00cck\u00e0nn\u00ec, and notifies you with this automated \u00cdme\u00e8l\u00ec.\n###CAUSE###\nFirst, visit your \u00cck\u00e0nn\u00ec (###SITEURL###) and check for any visible issues. Next, visit the Oj\u00faew\u00e9 where the error was caught (###PAGEURL###) and check for any visible issues.\n\n###SUPPORT###\n\nIf your \u00cck\u00e0nn\u00ec appears broken and you can't \u00ccgb\u00e0\u00e0y\u00e8 your dashboard normally, WordPress now has a special \"recovery mode\". This lets you safely login to your dashboard and investigate further.\n\n###\u00ccJ\u00c1P\u1ecc\u0300###\n\nTo keep your \u00cck\u00e0nn\u00ec safe, this \u00ccj\u00e1p\u1ecd\u0300 will expire in ###EXPIRES###. Don't worry about that, though: a Tuntun \u00ccj\u00e1p\u1ecd\u0300 will be emailed to you if the error occurs again after it expires.\n\nWhen seeking help with this issue, you may be asked for some of the following information:\n###DEBUG###\n\n###DETAILS###"],"media":["M\u00edd\u00ed\u00e0"],"no title":["R\u00e1r\u00e1 \u00c0k\u1ecdl\u00e9"],"Howdy,\n\nA user data privacy request has been confirmed on ###SITENAME###:\n\nUser: ###USER_EMAIL###\nRequest: ###DESCRIPTION###\n\nYou can view and manage these data privacy requests here:\n\n###MANAGE_URL###\n\nRegards,\nAll at ###SITENAME###\n###SITEURL###":["Howdy,\n\nA Ol\u00f9l\u00f2 data privacy request has been confirmed on ###SITENAME###:\n\nOl\u00f9l\u00f2: ###OL\u00d9L\u00d2_\u00cdME\u00c8L\u00cc###\nRequest: ###\u00c0P\u00c8J\u00daWE###\n\nYou can Wo and manage these data privacy requests here:\n\n###MANAGE_